{"tid":1542881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國歡迎香港政府撤回修例 盼香港進行有意義對話","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T13:36:34.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9bac32df588830002def0402350ebadaa3c7755d","tid":1542881,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8B%B1%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%9B%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-215743807.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1-215743807.html&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e1cd6a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8B%B1%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%9B%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-215743807.html</a><br />\n英國外相拉布(Dominic Raab)4日對香港特區行政長官林鄭月娥，撤回修訂已在這個前英國殖民地引發數月抗爭的逃犯條例草案表示歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n英國表歡迎<br />\n<br />\n拉布發表聲明說，這是受到歡迎的建立信心之舉。「我希望這能促成香港政府和其所服務的人民之間，進行有意義的對話。」<br />\n<br />\n針對港人陳同佳在台灣殺害同行女友並逃返香港，港府年初提出修訂逃犯條例，且適用於台灣、中國大陸和澳門，但泛民方面極力反對，稱之為「送中」條例。<br />\n<br />\n由於香港政府推動修訂逃犯條例引起反彈聲浪，香港民眾接連大規模示威抗議，警民暴力衝突受到全球關注。面臨港人強力反彈，林鄭月娥已宣佈暫緩修訂逃犯條例，但抗議團體要求她下台，並且正式撤回逃犯條例修訂案。<br />\n<br />\n港特首撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥是在4日下午發表電視公告，宣佈撤回修訂逃犯條例，並提出4項行動希望打破困局，表示她和司局長將會走入社區，聆聽市民心聲；邀請專家學者研究房屋土地供應、貧富懸殊、青少年上流、社會公義等深層次問題。<br />\n<br />\n但泛民主派平台民間人權陣線表示，他們將會繼續抗爭，直到五大訴求都落實。<br />\n<br />\n反送中示威者提出的五大訴求是：撤回逃犯條例修訂、成立獨立調查委員會、收回示威活動的暴動定性、撤銷對所有抗爭者的控罪以及立即實行雙真普選(行政長官和立法會選舉全面普選)。<br />\n<br />\n原始連結"},{"pid":"4617ba0affefbdcc730c14a0333687db308cdae0","tid":1542881,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563c132408163a6273f73005f678bf78a707fb23","tid":1542881,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm